":"DCMEx2kSGqpVu5LQLJm8_w","children":[]},{"id":"364","parent":"360","text":"✔️ Craniectomía descompresiva recomendada en herniación","guid":"EwZlwlkjPPMcj4PrbcLjjQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"365","parent":"341","text":"📌 8️⃣ Pronóstico","guid":"b5DoWwnkk8dYVRe9Ep-tUg","children":[{"id":"366","parent":"365","text":"✔️ Mortalidad baja (1-4% intrahospitalaria, 8-10% a largo plazo)","guid":"GpJkq0ln-xhfkuphGvUBXQ","children":[]},{"id":"367","parent":"365","text":"✔️ Secuelas persistentes en 68% (cefalea, déficits neuropsicológicos, crisis epilépticas)","guid":"MtwGPB9zZERwiQk4BMjLLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"368","parent":"341","text":"📌 IMPORTANTE:","guid":"S9PpHVW1pchpYWAtO2TReQ","children":[{"id":"369","parent":"368","text":"✔️ CVT tiene pronóstico favorable con diagnóstico y tratamiento oportuno","guid":"UoQvqSWkEBE5OtabMDdB_Q","children":[]},{"id":"370","parent":"368","text":"✔️ DOACs han cambiado el manejo de CVT","guid":"eCpQ7QtVewodm6tzFPuiDw","children":[]},{"id":"371","parent":"368","text":"✔️ Importancia de sospecha clínica y uso de neuroimagen avanzada","guid":"AGlgF3-F_DQc9RlaDIxk3g","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":371,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"Continuum. Diagnóstico y tratamiento de la trombosis venosa cerebral-2025","id":"map_273","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Continuum. Diagnóstico y tratamiento de la trombosis venosa cerebral-2025"}